\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Inherent Worth (
\f3\i Sokushin J\uc0\u333 butsu
\f0\i0 ):
\f1\b0  Shingon provides a foundational philosophical remedy for conditional self-worth by asserting that value is inherent, universal, and non-negotiable (
\f2\i Rigu no Jobutsu
\f1\i0 ).\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
