\f3\i Sanmitsu
\f0\i0 ):
\f1\b0  The coordination of Body (Mudr\uc0\u257 ), Speech (Mantra), and Mind (Mandala) offers an active, three-dimensional methodology for achieving deep concentration (
\f2\i samadhi
\f1\i0 ) and presence, directly countering digital burnout and fragmented attention.\
\ls1\ilvl0
