\fs24 \cf0 Core Concept:
\f1\b0  
\f2\i Sokushin J\uc0\u333 butsu
\f1\i0  (
\f2\i Rigu no Jobutsu
\f1\i0 )\'97Inherent, Unconditional Self-Worth.\

\f0\b Proposed Title/Concept:
